        "\n",
        "- `Accuracy`\n",
        "- `Precision`\n",
        "- `Recall`\n",
        "- `F1Score`\n",
        "- `ROC_AUC` when a probability column is available\n",
        "- Evidently HTML and JSON model quality report artifacts\n",
        "- `model_quality_summary.json` with the exact S3 files used\n"
      ]
    },
